refentry.refsect1:
&reftitle.parameters;




   string



     A modified UTF-7 encoding string, as defined in RFC 2060, section 5.1.3.

&reftitle.returnvalues;


 Returns a string that is encoded in ISO-8859-1 and consists of the same
 sequence of characters in string, or &false;
 if string contains invalid modified UTF-7 sequence
 or string contains a character that is not part of
 ISO-8859-1 character set.
